(define-minor-mode ajsc-interaction-mode
  "Minor mode for ajsc interaction from a lisp buffer.

The following keys are available in `ajsc-interaction-mode`:

\\{ajsc-interaction-mode}"
  :init-value nil
  :lighter " ajsc"
  :keymap ajsc-interaction-mode-map)

